title: DIRTY JURONG EAST BUS PARK SHOWS POOR ATTITUDE OF BUS CAPTAINS
text:
DIRTY JURONG EAST BUS PARK SHOWS POOR ATTITUDE OF BUS CAPTAINS   Advertisement 
Jurong East temporary bus interchange is so gross. So much litter at the bus parks. 
Since public are not allowed in the bus parks, it is very obvious that the rubbish on the ground is all contributed by the bus captains. If they can litter so freely even at their own workplace, I am skeptical of whether they even bother to keep public areas clean outside of working hours, with simple gestures such as throwing their own rubbish into rubbish bins. 
Anonymous X
